author: yuanchao
body:
#### PR description:

Similar to #41906, this PR adds comparison plots of two different tags for JetResolutionObject payload inspector. Jet parameters can be set through the input parameter interface of PI.

#### PR validation:

Locally tested with getPayloadData.py script.

#### If this PR is a backport please specify the original PR and why you need to backport that PR. If this PR will be backported please specify to which release cycle the backport is meant for:

This is not a backport.
title: Add comparison plots for JetResolution and SF
